snippet.title: Sweet F. Cake (EN) - Alice
snippet.description:
Alice
A tragic character. A sweet, shy girl in a strange life situation. Serge and Alice have been in the same class since 1st grade but don’t know each other. At some point, the hero notices her and tries to help. Saving the girl is not easy: a terrifying secret comes to light.
#sweetcake #texic #визуальная_новелла #сладкий_кексик #эччи
